### Notification API Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/notification-api

### Get My Notifications
GET http://localhost:5000/notification-api/my-notifications
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### Get Unread Count
GET http://localhost:5000/notification-api/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### Mark Notification as Read
PUT http://localhost:5000/notification-api/mark-read/NOTIFICATION_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN
